title: The Orb - 4orbidden Mission (3xCDR) (FLAC)
description:
This is a very rare and probably very unofficial numbered 3xCDR that functions as a kind of compilation of The Orb.

It features unique and long mixes of tracks from their first two albums, and is supposed to be from 2004.

There is almost no info about this anywhere, and I was lucky enough to find these FLAC-files on Soulseek.

If you have any information about this compilation or where the mixes are from, please write it in the comments.

And if you like The Orb's music, please go to their gigs and support them.
